WEBVTT

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:32.216
even if the most powerful person
in my world says that I shouldn't.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:34.416
Even if there's something hinky going on."

00:12:34.440 --> 00:12:36.136
That can make all the difference.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:38.696
